      <title>韩国尹正将与反对派领导人会面，寻求重置总统职位</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-yoon-meet-opposition-leader-amid-bid-reset-presidency-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹石烈将于周一与反对党领袖李在明进行会谈，此前总统执政党在选举中惨败，导致人们普遍呼吁他改变领导风格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-yoon-meet-opposition-leader-amid-bid-reset-presidency-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 01:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾学生因酷热而萎靡不振，教育工作受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-students-suffer-wilting-heat-thwarting-education-efforts-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾的酷热天气不仅会抑制农业生产、中断水电并给企业带来压力，还会对学生造成影响，阻碍这个东南亚国家在教育领域赶上邻国的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-students-suffer-wilting-heat-thwarting-education-efforts-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 01:01:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SK Innovation预计第二季度炼油利润稳定，电池部门亏损扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/sk-innovation-expects-solid-refining-margin-continue-q2-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国最大炼油商 SK Energy 的所有者 SK Innovation Co Ltd 周一表示，在需求强劲的支撑下，预计第二季度炼油利润率将继续保持稳健。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/sk-innovation-expects-solid-refining-margin-continue-q2-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 00:09:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>明星娱乐主席福斯特辞职，加剧管理层外流</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/star-entertainment-executive-chair-foster-steps-down-adds-management-exodus-2024-04-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[星娱乐公司周一表示，董事长戴维·福斯特(David Foster)已卸任一年多，这家陷入困境的澳大利亚赌场运营商的高级管理人员也纷纷离开。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/star-entertainment-executive-chair-foster-steps-down-adds-management-exodus-2024-04-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 23:39:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡电信预计减值额达 23 亿美元，2024 年下半年净亏损</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/singtel-expects-report-loss-2024-second-half-flags-23-bln-impairment-2024-04-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡电信周一预计 2024 年下半年的非现金减值准备金为 31 亿新元（22.8 亿美元），这将导致该电信巨头报告该期间的净亏损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/singtel-expects-report-loss-2024-second-half-flags-23-bln-impairment-2024-04-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 22:28:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保险公司友邦保险 (AIA) 第一季​​度新业务价值增长 31%，宣布回购 20 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/insurer-aias-first-quarter-new-business-value-rises-31-announces-2-billion-2024-04-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总部位于香港的保险公司友邦保险集团周一公布，由于各业务部门的强劲表现，其第一季度新业务价值（VONB）按固定汇率计算增长了 31%，并宣布额外回购 20 亿美元的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/insurer-aias-first-quarter-new-business-value-rises-31-announces-2-billion-2024-04-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 22:13:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝中社称，朝鲜批评美国向乌克兰提供远程导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korea-criticizes-us-supplying-long-range-missiles-ukraine-kcna-says-2024-04-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官方媒体朝中社周一援引国防部的声明报道称，朝鲜批评美国向乌克兰提供远程导弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korea-criticizes-us-supplying-long-range-missiles-ukraine-kcna-says-2024-04-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 21:46:44 GMT</pubDate>
